Quote:  <i>trots</i>: (A) MONTEZUMA'S REVENGE. (B) That pursuit in which horses pull small carts containing individuals around in circles in front of a large number of other people who have come to see them go round in circles and who place bets on which horse, cart and drier will go round fastest. HARNESS RACING.
